# Clinical Rotation in Reproductive Medicine

This is a Next.js (App Router, TypeScript) + Supabase learning platform: "Clinical Rotation in Reproductive Medicine". Audiences: medical students, new-start doctors, nurses.

## Specs

- Follow `docs/PLATFORM_BUILD_SPEC.md` and `docs/PLATFORM_BUILD_v1.1_phase0.md`.
- Content assets live in `content/`. Brand tokens live in `docs/brand-tokens.css`.

## Stack

- Use `@supabase/ssr` for auth, Tailwind for styling, and the tokens in `docs/brand-tokens.css`.
- Keep all secrets in environment variables, never in code.

## Security & privacy (non-negotiable)

- Enforce row-level security on every table.
- Never store patient-identifiable data.
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` is server/scripts only — never expose to the browser.

## Working style

- Work in small, reviewable steps.
- After each change, tell the user how to test it.
